rComments: Quizs are very simple, but the exams and experiments are very difficult. Too hard for me.

He is one of the best professors I have seen. He is very understanding and explains the material clearly. He makes you work hard for a good grade, which in my opinion is the right way to do in a competitive world.
A very good prof in general.  Close your eyes and listen, and you will hear a French-accented version of Kermit the frog teaching engineering.
A very intelligent and knowledgable teacher. One of the best professors in SITE. Once you read his notes you'll understand why.
